name: Tea or Death
description: "Take some more tea, " the March Hare said to Alice, very earnestly. "I've had nothing yet," Alice replied in an offending tone: "so I can't take more." "You mean you can't take less ," said the Hatter: "it's very easy to take more than nothing." - Lewis Carroll A shirt celebrating the Queen's Caffeine. A present for the women in our lives, without whom, we would be better known as October Crumble. -Light Grey artwork on high-end women's poly/cotton crew (navy) -Slightly heathered, and ultra soft -Women's tees run small, so order a size up to ensure a good fit. -Available in S (sold out!), M (sold out), L (sold out), XL(sold out!), XXL

name: No Trust
description: Let every eye negotiate for itself, and trust no agent. - Shakespeare October Built would be remiss if we did not recognize the impact 1982 had on our development. The amount of quality pop cinema released in those twelve months was so saturated, it nearly defined an entire adolescent generation within only the second year of the decade. Among the many masterpieces that year, we were given one of the greatest horror movies ever made, by a visionary at the top of his game. We pay homage to him, and to all that shaped us. -White artwork on high-end, poly/cotton crew (black) -ultra soft -Available in S (sold out!), M, L, XL, XXL

name: Death to Ming - Red Ringer
description: This Ming is a psycho. - Flash Gordon While October Built does not typically espouse the wisdom of quarterbacks, Flash was right. Ming the Merciless was a genocidal maniac, and nothing, not even a cool beard (or cool eyebrows, or a cool right-hand man, or cool golden-skull masks for your soldiers (that have cool choking ray gun things)) can make up for that fact (it totally makes up for that fact). Protest his tyranny from the safety of a planet far from Mongo, where Ming's minions do not scout. Hell, most Earthlings won't even know who you're talking about - But October Built knows. October Built knows. - Red artwork on preshrunk 100% heavyweight cotton - Classic white ringer tee with red collar and sleeves - Available in S, M, L (sold out!), XL (sold out!), XXL (sold out!)
